*   **Historical Parallel:** **Victorian Textile Mills.** We remember the fire at the Triangle Shirtwaist Factory and the sweatshop conditions of the 19th century. Fast fashion is simply that system, digitized and globalized.

### 4. Surveillance Capitalism (Attention Economy)
**The Verdict:** *The Weaponization of Human Psychology*

*   **Why it will be seen as Barbaric:** We currently allow companies to harvest intimate human data, analyze our vulnerabilities, and manipulate our dopamine loops to sell us things. In 100 years, this will be viewed not as "business," but as **psychological enslavement**. Violating the cognitive liberty of children and adults alike for ad revenue will be seen as a violation of the right to self-determination.
