### 5. Single-Use Plastics & Non-Degradable Packaging
**The Verdict:** *Pollution by Design*

*   **Why it will be seen as Barbaric:** Creating materials that persist for a thousand years for a product used for five minutes will be seen as the height of irrationality. The Great Pacific Garbage Patches and the contamination of deep-sea vents with microplastics will be the evidence of a civilization that refused to accept its responsibility for waste.
