The most effective opposition to **The Covenant of Earth** will not come from a single villain, but from a **Coalition of Incumbent Power**. This coalition consists of **Major Nation-States** (specifically the UN Security Council permanent members and emerging economic powers), **Legacy Industrial Conglomerates** (fossil fuels, agribusiness, defense), and **Nationalist Populist Movements**.

This coalition is effective because it controls the three levers of reality: **Political Sovereignty**, **Economic Capital**, and **Public Narrative**.

Here is how they would oppose the framework, and what they would argue.

---

### I. The Opposition Coalition

