*   **Resource Hoarding:** The diversion of finite hydrocarbons to make disposable bottles will be seen as a gross misuse of finite planetary resources.

### 4. The Attention Economy & Behavioral Profiling
**Current Practice:** Technology companies building platforms designed to maximize engagement by exploiting psychological vulnerabilities, addicting users to their own devices, and harvesting intimate data to sell targeted ads.
**The Future Judgment:**
