### 1. From "Ego to Eco" $\rightarrow$ "The Integrated Ego"
The first version treated the "Ego" (ambition, dominance, individualism) as a bug to be overwritten. I now realize the Ego is the engine of human progress. If you suppress it, you create a stagnant civilization that is easily conquered.

